'''Coruscant Park''' was a large park located near the [[Jedi Temple/Legends|Jedi Temple]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Masters]] often took their [[Padawan/Legends|Padawans]] to the Park for meditation.

